      <groundspeak:long_description html="True">&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Comic Sans MS,cursive;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:14px;"&gt;We are heading for Big Red and thought we would stop by and see the World&amp;#39;s Largest Covered Porch Swing. Join us swingers as we sway to and fro talking about geocaching and the Mega event in Hutchison KS. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

