        <groundspeak:log id="1353876357">
          <groundspeak:date>2026-04-08T02:50:03Z</groundspeak:date>
          <groundspeak:type>Attended</groundspeak:type>
          <groundspeak:finder id="8814283">TheLF</groundspeak:finder>
          <groundspeak:text encoded="False">Decided to visit the Upper Mid-States after the recent messy weather passed through. A pleasant change from the already 80s &amp; 90s in Florida. Then I spied this event in Nebraska. I need an event in NE, so I signed up..🤣. 
Thanks statsharon &amp; peteach for hosting this lively group. Everything was great… the food, fellowship, and PathTag trades too. It was a fun time. 
That is the event trifecta..😎. Again, thank you for the warm welcome to this stranger in town.
Hoping to see some familiar faces at GeoWoodstock in Hutchinson later  this year. Happy caching y’all..!</groundspeak:text>
        </groundspeak:log>
